A photo of booty at the very same location in the LOC/Bain photostream.  Accordingly, the caption should read &quot;Neufmontiers.&quot;
[http://www.flickr.com/photos/library_of_congress/6197571059/]

Interestingly, there's a sapling in the photo with the Turcos that has disappeared in this photo with the French soldiers.  Also, there is an impressive pile of rifles in this photo (see lower left side of the frame) that wasn't there when the photo of the Turcos was taken.
